ture, but it's never a purely theoretical debate. You really come to question what is actually best for this child. In a good way. ","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/605205?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/11562887"},"likeCount":11,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.dR-AAydo-X2nBxchOMqHPQ":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.dR-AAydo-X2nBxchOMqHPQ","__typename":"Work","legacyId":161123,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.ijWp_EFPe9e1_3LuEF8--A"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/161123-pigs-in-heaven","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/161123-pigs-in-heaven","publicationTime":725875200000,"originalTitle":"Pigs in Heaven","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Los Angeles Times Book Prize","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/3812-los-angeles-times-book-prize","awardedAt":725875200000,"category":"Fiction","hasWon":true}],"places":[],"characters":[]},"reviews":{"__typename":"BookReviewsConnection","totalCount":2272,"edges":[{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.QoSepn6tRrJxXawPuuhjyg"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.lj07SAQ6l6j_oLgaD-tPSg"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.ReeizUWj6TmOpkqXT5IwYA"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.TItu3x2EJN5TqwFPF_OT9A"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.E_8xyIPOCaLcje5TAqRc2w"}},{"__typename":"BookReviewsEdge","node":{"__ref":"Review:kc